doctype html
html(lang="en")
    head
        meta(charset="UTF-8")
        meta(name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
        link(rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css")
        title Order Failed
    body
        
        include navbar.pug
        
        .failure-container
            h1 Transaction Failed
            p Your request could not be processed by the server.
            
            p This typically occurs due to one of the following reasons:
            ul
                li **Missing Data:** You did not fill out all the required fields on the order form.
                li **Invalid Order ID:** The order ID submitted (for cancellation or update) was not found.
                li **Ineligible Status:** You attempted to cancel or update an order that has already been **Delivered** or **Cancelled**.

            p Please use the links below to navigate back:
            .failure-actions
                a.button-link(href="/order") Try Placing a New Order
                a.button-link(href="/admin/order")  View All Orders (Admin)